ZH: 请把电灯关掉。
EN: Please turn off the light.

ZH: 我每天晚上睡觉前都会打开电灯。
EN: I always turn on the light before going to bed every night.

ZH: 电灯坏了，我得换个新的。
EN: The light bulb is broken, I need to replace it with a new one.

ZH: 我家里有很多不同款式的电灯。
EN: There are many different styles of light fixtures in my house.

ZH: 在停电时，我们总是使用手电筒代替电灯。
EN: During a power outage, we always use a flashlight instead of the light bulb.

ZH: 这个房间的电灯太刺眼了，我想换个暖色的。
EN: The light in this room is too bright, I want to change it to a warmer color.

ZH: 老师说我们要节约用电，所以不要随便开电灯。
EN: The teacher said we should save electricity, so don't turn on the light unnecessarily.

ZH: 我家的客厅有一个很漂亮的水晶吊灯作为主要电灯。
EN: There is a beautiful crystal chandelier in the living room of my house as the main light fixture.

ZH: 她在书桌上放了一个小的台灯，用于阅读时点亮。
EN: She placed a small desk lamp on the desk to turn on when reading.

ZH: 学生要在晚上的夜间阅读时，最好使用柔和的电灯。
EN: When students are reading at night, it is best to use soft light bulbs.

ZH: 我刚刚在书房里换了新的LED电灯。
EN: I just replaced the old light bulb in the study with a new LED light.

ZH: 公园里的路灯是太阳能电灯，可以在夜晚自动点亮。
EN: The street lights in the park are solar-powered, they can automatically turn on at night.

ZH: 每个床头都放了一个小夜灯，用于夜间起床时不照亮整个房间。
EN: A small night light is placed at each bedside so that it doesn't illuminate the entire room when getting up at night.

ZH: 这间餐厅的特色是吊灯和墙上的小电灯。
EN: The featured of this restaurant are the chandeliers and the small wall lights.

ZH: 他不喜欢在黑暗中睡觉，所以床头有一盏灯可随时点亮。
EN: He doesn't like to sleep in the dark, so there is a light on the bedside to turn on anytime.

ZH: 在这个地方，太阳落下后我们只能开电灯照明。
EN: In this place, we can only turn on the light for illumination after the sun sets.

ZH: 他在阅读前都会打开写字台的小吸顶灯。
EN: He always turns on the small ceiling light on the desk before reading.

ZH: 教室里的黑板上有一排一排的荧光灯作为主要电灯。
EN: In the classroom, there are rows of fluorescent tubes on the blackboard as the main light fixtures.

ZH: 在这个地方，夜晚会开放灯光秀，让游客欣赏美丽的电灯艺术。
EN: In this place, there will be a light show at night for visitors to enjoy the beautiful light art.

ZH: 他们在花园里的树上挂了很多彩色电灯，让整个空间更加浪漫。
EN: They hung many colored light bulbs on the trees in the garden to make the entire space more romantic.
